com.smartgov.lez.core.agent.establishment

Class Round

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.smartgov.lez.core.agent.establishment.Round

  • public class Round
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a round that a delivery agent might perform between establishments.

    Notice that this class does not represent the actual path that the agent could follow in the city graph : is just represents the establishment list that it must deliver.
